      <title>Apollo 利润因费用增长和私人信贷增长而跃升 26%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/apollo-profit-jumps-26-on-fee-growth-private-credit-strength</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 报告第一季度利润更高，因为该公司获得了更多管理费，并发放了创纪录的 400 亿美元私人信贷，这是增长的关键领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/apollo-profit-jumps-26-on-fee-growth-private-credit-strength</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
